title: Friday Feast!
description: PA & Charch lament the Wild losing game 3 last night, talk in more detail about it with GM Bill Guerin at the end of the first hour. Chad Greenway makes his weekly appearance, Tenna B begins the final hour with more Wild opinions, and talkers to close!
